          "description": "I love this pharmacy. I started at their Avenue B location, which was right up the block from where I lived. That location is amazing as well. I was moving and told them that I was very upset because I was moving and the Avenue B location was too far for me to go to for my medication. They asked me where I was moving to and when I told them they told me about the Clinton Street location which is right up the block from where I live now. I couldn't be happier. I've been with them for many many years and every time I go in for my refills they greet me personally and with smiles. I highly recommend either location. They are very helpful \ud83d\udc4c",
